The paper deals with transfer learning, which is a common topic in machine learning and falls under the category of "Learning" (cs.LG). However, the paper specifically applies transfer learning to two domains: images (cs.CV) and semantic relations (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper uses a measure called "Predict To Learn" (P2L), which involves predicting the effectiveness of transfer learning models, and this could potentially fall under the categories of "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) or "Information Retrieval" (cs.IR).
